David,

Is this your way of saying there is a difference with resto using OG VW
parts, and say, VW/Brazilian/Mexican parts?  Would you include other
aftermarket components in the second level, or would that be altogether
a third level of "resto?"  I can see the logic.

There certainly needs to be an "all original" OG VW parts resto to
